resetStubModifiedDates(Set<File>) - Method in class gmavenplus.mojo.AbstractGenerateStubsMojo
This is a fix for fix for http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MGROOVY-187 It modifies the dates of the created stubs to 1970, ensuring that the Java compiler will not come along and overwrite perfectly good compiled Groovy just because it has a newer source stub.
